HEADWORD: Expulse
<hw>Ex*pulse"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>expulser</ets> or L. <ets>expulsare</ets>, intens. fr.
<ets>expellere</ets>. See <er>Expel</er>.]</ety> <def>To drive out; to
